blockedtext-partial: Block aka wo din anaa IP address ɛnti wo ntumi nnyɛ ayi. wo bɛtumi ayɛ biriri foforo bi, ti sɛ wo bɛ sesa nktratafa bi. Wobɛtumi ahwɛ block no ho asɛm ɛwɔ [[Special:MyContributions|account contributions]]. $1 na ɛyɛ block no. Nea ɛnti ɔyɛ block no ɛne sɛ $2. * Block no mfiase: $8 * Da block no ɛbɛ wu: $6 * Nea block no ɛyɛ no de: $7 * Block no hyɛnso de #$5
blockedtext: Yɛ de block ato wo din anaa IP address no so. Nea ɔyɛ block no yɛ $1. Nea ɛnti a ɔyɛ block no ɛne sɛ $2. * Block no mfiase: $8 * Da block no ɛbɛ wu: $6 * Nea block no ɛyɛ no de: $7 Wobɛtumi ne $1 anaa [[{{MediaWiki:Grouppage-sysop}}|administrator]] ɛdi block no ho nkɔmɔ. Wobɛtumi de "{{int:emailuser}}" ayɛ adwuma sɛ wo wɔ email address a ɛyɛ adwuma a block ɛnka no wɔ wo [[Special:Preferences|preferences]] mu. Wo IP address a wo de yɛ adwuma no yɛ $3, ɛna block no ahyɛnso de no yɛ #$5. Sɛ wo wɔ asɛm bisa bia, fa saa nkyerɛkyerɛmu yi nyinaa ka ho.
